          <p>After moving to New York City for The Daily Show, Oliver began performing stand-up in small clubs around
            the city
            and
            later headlined shows in larger venues. Oliver's first stand-up special, titled John Oliver: Terrifying
            Times,
            debuted on Comedy Central in 2008 and was later released on DVD.Since 2010, Oliver has hosted four seasons
